thread.title_full: BRIEF-Gemalto announces launch of Cinterion secure element | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Gemalto announces launch of Cinterion secure element
text:
Sept 14 Gemalto NV :
* Launches Cinterion secure element for protection of automotive and industrial Internet of Things (IoT) solutions
* Solution offers protection against extreme environmental conditions and is tamper resistant
Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
